summary.label:
Face Swap Live lets you switch faces with a friend or a photo in real-time.  Record videos or photos of yourself swapping faces with a celebrity, friend or any fun picture from the internet or your phone. Unlike other apps that only can use static photos, this app switches faces live right from your camera’s video feed. 

Ever wanted to see your talking face on Marilyn Monroe’s photo. Be amazed putting your moving mouth onto a pic of your favorite pet.

== As Featured on the TODAY Show with Kathy Lee and Hoda! ==


** TIPS for good face swapping videos **

1. Position: Don't tilt or rotate your head, or move around too quickly.
2. Good lighting: Make sure your faces are not too dark, also avoid very bright lights coming from behind.
3. Brush back any hair that might be around your eyes.
4. Remove glasses if possible; large beards can also cause some shaking.
